"<li><samp>&lt;Unit X not placed&gt;</samp> - Pin is in a unit not placed on "
"any sheet</li>\n"
"<li><samp>&lt;Unresolved: Cell X not found&gt;</samp> - Cell address is out "
"of table bounds</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
